  "description": "Designed to track synthesiser pads and sustained tones. Moderate selectivity covers the midrange swell. Slow reactivity smooths over filter sweeps and vibrato, extracting only the overall amplitude contour. Long memory sustains the coupling signal across the body of each note, creating stable sidechain pressure from held chords.",
